# Operator service: pause / resume a running long-lived campaign tree.
#
# Pause sets `persistent.paused = true` so the BlackboardCondition gate at
# the top of the campaign loop short-circuits the next iteration. Any
# in-flight cycle finishes naturally — never killed mid-transfer.
#
# Resume sets the flag back to false. The same service is used for both;
# inspect `paused` to choose.

bool paused                    # true → pause, false → resume
string reason                  # recorded to operator_events
---
bool success
string message
